This toolkit wraps the following upstream projects, each under its own license:
  - Video2X (k4yt3x/video2x) — GPLv3, https://github.com/k4yt3x/video2x
  - Upscale-A-Video (sczhou/Upscale-A-Video) — see upstream LICENSE
  - Real-ESRGAN community models (upscayl, NMKD, foolhardy, etc.) — see each model card

Distribute the wrappers and Dockerfile under this MIT license; the upstream
container images and model weights retain their original licenses.
